	(text_box "Do not supply power to the +Vdd pin of the ISP connector when the module's USB plug is connected to the PC!\n\nDo not supply power to the +Vdd pin of the FTDI module without first disconnecting its on-board voltage selection jumper to ensure the IC's Vcc-IO is not powered from both the PC and this board!"
